{
  "stem": "107.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I am not bragging with it because there is some heaviness in it. --came another transport in our camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my parents were in this transport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In a way, when they were-- when they heard that they go to this new camp where her son already is for half a year, they were happy.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So finally we will get together.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Of course, when they came to Birkenau, they were less happy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So what I did immediately, I tried to help them by giving them some clothes that I could organize.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's a word that was used there, and you either steal it, or get it in exchange with a favor to somebody else.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And a doctor is always willing to give some favors maybe in the future.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So if I come and say, do you have an old rag, or sweaters or shoes, they will give it to me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was pretty hard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean, my father was then in his 50s, or maybe closer to 60.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My mother was seven or six years  younger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But you know, for Birkenau that is already beyond the tolerable stage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My mother got immediately this terrible diarrhea, where the people died from it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But I could arrange her to be taken to the hospital, so she could last a little longer.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "My father, who is-- a creative-- was a very creative person, found immediately some activity for himself.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "People had lost their glasses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were half blind.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Through the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He took them in and said, we have some glasses.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He found some glasses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He got glasses.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then, of course, there were ten thousands of glasses of people who were executed.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
